<div class="grid-container">
  <div id="fullpage">
    <div class="section" id="offers">
      <div class="slide" id="slide1" data-anchor="slideOne">

        <div class="offers-container">
          <h1 class="offers-title"><%= t(:offerOneTitle) %></h1>
          <p class="offers-intro"><%= t(:offerOneIntro) %></p>

          <div class="offers-group has-three-col">
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Basis für DevOps</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Professioneller Partner für Backup, Monitoring, Updates und 7x24 Support</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Small - Medium - Large: Auf Sie zugeschnittene Angebote</article>
          </div>

          <p class="offers-services-desc"><%= t(:offerOneServicesDesc) %></p>

          <div class="offers-group">
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Consulting Setup und Initialisierung</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Bring my App to the Cloud - wir beraten und setzen auch um</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Automatisierung Ihrer Prozesse: Continuos Delivery und Continuous Deployment Ihrer Applikationen</article>
          </div>

          <h3 class="offers-package-title">Wählen Sie das für Ihre Bedürfnisse passende Paket:</h3>

          <div class="offers-package-container">
            <article class="offers-package">
              <h3 class="offers-package-list-title">Small</h3>
              <ul class="offers-package-list">
                <li class="offers-package-item">1 Master (je 4GB Ram, 2vCores)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">2 Nodes(je 16 GB Ram, 6VCores, 100 GB Docker Storage)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">200 GB Persistent Storage</li>
              </ul>
            </article>
            <article class="offers-package">
              <h3 class="offers-package-list-title">Medium</h3>
              <ul class="offers-package-list">
                <li class="offers-package-item">3 Master (je 4GB Ram, 2vCores)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">4 Nodes (je 16 GB Ram, 6VCores, 100 GB Docker Storage)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">500 GB Persistent Storage</li>
              </ul>
            </article>
            <article class="offers-package">
              <h3 class="offers-package-list-title">Large</h3>
              <ul class="offers-package-list">
                <li class="offers-package-item">3 Master (je 4GB Ram, 2vCores)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">8 Nodes (je 16 GB Ram, 6VCores, 100 GB Docker Storage)</li>
                <li class="offers-package-item">1 TB Persistent Storage</li>
              </ul>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="slide" id="slide2" data-anchor="slideTwo">

        <div class="offers-container">
          <h1 class="offers-title"><%= t(:homeOfferTwoTitle) %></h1>
          <p class="offers-intro">Sie brauchen kurzfristig standardisierte Entwicklungsressourcen oder möchten Ihre produktive Applikation bei Bedarf skalieren?</p>
          <div class="offers-group">
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Auf Ihre Bedürfnisse zugeschnittene Bundles</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Von Entwicklern für Entwickler: Forum, Dokumentation und Community</article>
            <article class="offers-item is-turkislight">Wir kümmern uns um Backup, Monitoring, Updates und Support</article>
          </div>
          <p class="offers-services-desc">Ihre APPUiO Managed Private PaaS wird in ISO27001-zertifizierten und nach FINMA-Richtlinien gebauten Rechenzentren in der Schweiz betrieben und untersteht schweizerischem Recht.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="slide" id="slide3" data-anchor="slideThree">
        <h1><%= t(:homeOfferThreeTitle) %></h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- Section One fertig -->

    <div class="section" id="contacts">
      <div class="">
        <!-- TODO: Klassen anpassen -->
        <h2 class="home-contact-title">Kontakt</h2>
        <p class="home-contact-desc">Thomas Philippona, philipona@appuio.ch, Tel. XXX</p>

        <form id="contact-form" class="">
          <div class="home-contact-interest interest-container">
            <h3 class="interest-title">Gewünschtes Packet:</h3>
            <div class="interest-item">
              <input id="interest-cluster" value="<%= t(:offerContactOneSmall) %>" type="checkbox" name="interests[]" class="interest-checkbox">
              <label for="interest-cluster"><%= evil_icon 'ei-close', class: "interest-icon" %> <%= t(:offerContactOneSmall) %></label>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-item">
              <input id="interest-beta" value="<%= t(:offerContactOneMedium) %>" type="checkbox" name="interests[]" class="interest-checkbox">
              <label for="interest-beta"><%= evil_icon 'ei-close', class: "interest-icon" %> <%= t(:offerContactOneMedium) %></label>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-item">
              <input id="interest-paas" value="<%= t(:offerContactOneLarge) %>" type="checkbox" name="interests[]" class="interest-checkbox">
              <label for="interest-paas"><%= evil_icon 'ei-close', class: "interest-icon" %> <%= t(:offerContactOneLarge) %></label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="home-contact-form">
            <input title="<%= t(:homeContactYourFirstNameTitle) %>" type="text" name="vorname" class="contact-input" placeholder="<%= t(:homeContactYourFirstName) %>" required>
            <input title="<%= t(:homeContactYourNameTitle) %>" type="text" name="nachname" class="contact-input" placeholder="<%= t(:homeContactYourName) %>" required>
            <input type="email" name="email" class="contact-input" placeholder="<%= t(:homeContactYourEmail) %>" required>
            <textarea title="<%= t(:homeContactYourMessageTitle) %>" id="message" name="message" cols="30" rows="6" class="contact-textarea" placeholder="<%= t(:homeContactYourMessage) %>" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <label class="home-contact-button button-progress">
            <input type="submit" class="button is-round" value="<%= t(:homeContactSend) %>">
          </label>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section" id="footer">
      <%= partial "partials/footer" %>
    </div>

  </div> <!-- end fullpage div -->
</div> <!-- end grid-container
